OL,5, As the cost of living rises it is      
OL,6, "vital" that broadband firms do more to
OL,7, promote discounted broadband for       
OL,8, low-income households, the government  
OL,9, says.                                  
OL,11,FIn a letter to broadband suppliers,    
OL,12,FCulture Secretary Nadine Dorries noted 
OL,13,Fonly 1-2% of Universal Credit claimants
OL,14,Ftake up social tariffs.                
OL,16,FOfcom has previously said that 84% of  
OL,17,Fbenefit recipients were unaware of     
OL,18,Fsocial tariff packages.                
OL,20,FIt said it had seen "limited evidence" 
OL,21,Fof those tariffs being promoted.       
